  "texts": [
    "Out of the 984 publications listed on Scopus, 621 were published during this period.",
    "About 600 publications were available on the Web of Science, 300 of which were published between 2019 and 2024.",
    "Research Questions (RQs)In order to direct our investigation, precise Research Questions (RQs) have been developed and concepts to analyze research papers.",
    "In order to better comprehend how these approaches are created and used, we first looked at the many kinds of procedures that are employed.",
    "The evaluation of these techniques was then looked at, along with an introduction to their difficulties, the datasets that are employed, and lastly, the suggested direction for future research."
  ]
}